name: meautility
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "MEAutility" %}
{% set version = "1.5.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: de12cc9c1772d3321e941af78e6bfb36cdcb5702a7b1272a852cc95f413bbfcb

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: '{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv '

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - matplotlib-base
    - numpy
    - python >=3.6
    - pyyaml

test:
  requires:
    - pytest
  imports:
    - MEAutility
    - MEAutility.tests
  commands:
    - py.test -vsx --pyargs MEAutility

about:
  home: https://github.com/alejoe91/MEAutility
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Python package for multi-electrode array (MEA) handling and stimulation.
  doc_url: https://meautility.readthedocs.io/en/latest/
  dev_url: https://github.com/alejoe91/MEAutility

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - alejoe91
    - espenhgn
